## 8. Learning path PR reviews

For `-lj` packages (multiple milestones, manifest chains, live testing), use the dedicated five-phase workflow — not this single-guide checklist alone. **Human-in-the-loop:** the reviewer smoke-tests in Block Editor; the agent drafts comments for approval before posting.

- **Command:** [/review-learning-path-pr](commands/review-learning-path-pr.md)
- **Skill:** [review-learning-path](skills/review-learning-path/SKILL.md)
- **Comment voice:** [comment-style.md](skills/review-learning-path/comment-style.md)
- **Learning Hub criteria:** [learning-hub-standards.md](skills/review-learning-path/learning-hub-standards.md)

LP PRs are **single-repo** (`interactive-tutorials` only). Metadata lives in package `website.yaml` ([PR #416](https://github.com/grafana/interactive-tutorials/pull/416)).
